 {"id":"franken_networkx-tarjanlca","title":"PORT: Tarjan offline LCA native Rust impl","description":"Port the tree lowest-common-ancestor path from Python Tarjan union-find into native Rust while preserving NetworkX observable behavior. Breakthrough fit: Tarjan offline LCA with disjoint-set union gives near-linear batch LCA on rooted trees and maps directly to `tree_all_pairs_lowest_common_ancestor` and the existing DAG LCA surface. Success criteria: exact root selection, pair orientation/order, missing-node errors, null/undirected/cycle/tree-validation contracts, Python binding parity, and a focused parity test suite against upstream NetworkX.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-04-24T20:59:22Z","created_by":"codex","updated_at":"2026-04-24T20:59:22Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
